{"tid":2374500,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"坂本龍一再度患癌 已動手術治療中","createTime":"2021-01-21T09:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T11:31:24.000Z","uid":12836,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ebae15e65c86d630eef00cbd84002264978871","tid":2374500,"uid":12836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"69歲的日本知名作曲家坂本龍一今（21）日透過社群平台及官網，以英文、日文、中文曝光確診罹患直腸癌的消息，他表示在得知消後一度情緒消沉，不過在專業的醫護人員看護下，他已完成手術，持續治療中。<br />\n<br />\n因為健康狀況加上新冠疫情影響，坂本龍一表示自己目前無法出遠門，對於目前手頭上的工作，他在接受治療時也會儘力完成，但若情況不允許，他也不得不取消部分工作。坂本龍一為可能為他人帶來影響先行說抱歉。最後，他則說道：「此後的日子，我將『與癌共生』」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOuRhPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOuRhPm.jpg&h=2756cb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10088/5192407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Fstory%2F10088%2F5192407&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=0db362bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10088/5192407</a><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e569fc593b8142e92d58d4078519be1c3758ff6b","tid":2374500,"uid":12836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱先過咗生日 就搞啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d24463b1aa6f01b27ce9878b4dc44b712d4911","tid":2374500,"uid":12836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:20:47.000Z","msg"